# SPINE runtime data
# NB: the live vector index .spine/spine.db is ignored, but its committed,
# compressed snapshot .spine/spine.db.xz is NOT — that artifact is checked
# in so fresh clones restore the index instead of re-indexing. `*.db` / `*.xz`
# do not collide (.db.xz ends in .xz), so no negation rule is needed.
.spine/artifacts/
.spine/spine.db
.spine/queue.db
.spine/work_entries.db
.spine/jobs.db
.spine/state/
.spine/audit.db

